Achievements.Name: Eleven Calypso Pieces
Achievements.Description: Find the hidden Calypso piece on each level to unlock the story of Davy Jones and Calypso.

Achievements.Name: Seven Letters
Achievements.Description: Collect all seven Letters, lost throughout the Prison Fortress.

Achievements.Name: Seven Periwigs
Achievements.Description: Collect the seven Periwigs hidden around Port Royal.

Achievements.Name: Seven Nautilus Shells
Achievements.Description: Collect the seven Nautilus shells, scattered throughout the Flying Dutchman.

Achievements.Name: Seven Pirate Flags
Achievements.Description: Collect the seven Pirate Flags of Tortuga, hidden in chests and secret areas.

Achievements.Name: Seven Paprika Tins
Achievements.Description: Collect the seven Paprika tins of Isla Cruces.

Achievements.Name: Seven Bottles of Rum
Achievements.Description: Collect the seven bottles of Rum (hidden in the Black Pearl) during the Kraken's attack.

Achievements.Name: Seven Sea Charts
Achievements.Description: Collect the seven Sea Charts from the streets of Singapore.

Achievements.Name: Seven Skulls
Achievements.Description: Collect the seven Skulls hidden throughout Davy Jones' Locker.

Achievements.Name: Seven Tarot Cards
Achievements.Description: Collect the seven Tarot cards lost around the Flying Dutchman.

Achievements.Name: Seven Gold Bars
Achievements.Description: Gold - every pirate's dream! Collect the seven gold bars of Shipwreck City.

Achievements.Name: Seven Pirate's Dice
Achievements.Description: Collect the seven Pirate's dice, lost around the Flying Dutchman and the Black Pearl.

Achievements.Name: Prison Fortress Treasure
Achievements.Description: Open the Jackanism chest in the Prison Fortress, and unlock bonus material in the Treasure Trove.

Achievements.Name: Port Royal Treasure
Achievements.Description: Open the Jackanism chest in Port Royal, and unlock bonus material in the Treasure Trove.

Achievements.Name: Tortuga Treasure
Achievements.Description: Open the Jackanism chest of Tortuga, and unlock bonus material in the Treasure Trove.

Achievements.Name: Isla Cruces Treasure
Achievements.Description: Open the Jackanism chest in Isla Cruces, and unlock bonus material in the Treasure Trove.

Achievements.Name: The Kraken Treasure
Achievements.Description: Open the Jackanism chest in the Black Pearl, and unlock bonus material in the Treasure Trove.

Achievements.Name: Davy Jones' Locker Treasure
Achievements.Description: Open the Jackanism chest of Davy Jones' Locker, and unlock bonus material in the Treasure Trove.

Achievements.Name: Shipwreck City Treasure
Achievements.Description: Open the Jackanism chest in Shipwreck City, and unlock bonus material in the Treasure Trove.

Achievements.Name: The Maelstrom Treasure
Achievements.Description: Open the Jackanism chest of the Maelstrom, and unlock bonus material in the Treasure Trove.

Achievements.Name: Jack's second finish move
Achievements.Description: Unlock Jack's second finish move by escaping from the Prison Fortress.

Achievements.Name: Jack's third finish move
Achievements.Description: Unlock Jack's third finish move by surviving the Kraken's attack.

Achievements.Name: Jack's fourth finish move
Achievements.Description: Unlock Jack's fourth finish move by escaping from Davy Jones' Locker.

Achievements.Name: Will's second finish move
Achievements.Description: Unlock Will's second finish move by saving Chevalle and leaving Port Royal.

Achievements.Name: Will's third finish move
Achievements.Description: Unlock Will's third finish move by stealing the key from the Flying Dutchman.

Achievements.Name: Will's fourth finish move
Achievements.Description: Unlock Will's fourth finish move by surviving Isla Cruces.

Achievements.Name: Elizabeth's second finish move
Achievements.Description: Unlock Elizabeth's second finish move by locating Mistress Ching and Villanueva in Tortuga.

Achievements.Name: Elizabeth's third finish move
Achievements.Description: Unlock Elizabeth's third finish move by surviving Isla Cruces.

Achievements.Name: Elizabeth's fourth finish move
Achievements.Description: Unlock Elizabeth's fourth finish move by exploring and escaping from Singapore.

Achievements.Name: Collect 100 Souls
Achievements.Description: Collect one hundred souls from your enemies using the power of the Jackanism sword.
